00:23:25.120 --> 00:23:26.490
<i>Ayo mulai, Jiren!</i>

00:23:26.840 --> 00:23:28.840
<i>Selanjutnya di Dragon Ball Super!</i>

00:23:28.840 --> 00:23:32.220
<i>"Melampaui Batas Super!
Menguasai Insting Ultra!!"</i>

